						<summary>

						<p>States that a certain <hi rend="bold">[Rē]yamayyaru (?)</hi> erected a temple of the Sun and endowed it, on the occasion of a Solar Eclipse, with the permission of <hi rend="bold">Chōḍamahārāja</hi> with a piece of land and an oil-pressing mill.</p>						

